   - InvalidPasswordException, ContentTooLongException, etc.
   - These represent domain rule violations

2. Enhance Business Rules Constants (Domain Responsibility)
   - Ensure all business rules are captured in domain constants
   - Move magic numbers from entities into BusinessRules class
   - These represent core business policies

3. Add Domain Entity Factory Methods (Domain Responsibility)
   - User.Create() factory methods with proper validation
   - Post.Create() with hashtag extraction and validation
   - Ensure entities are created in valid states